DEOKPUNG VILLAGE SENIOR CENTER OPENING

238
00:12:47,266 --> 00:12:48,434
Magandang trabaho!

239
00:12:48,517 --> 00:12:50,811
- Ito ay kahanga-hangang!
- Ito ay gumagana nang maayos!

240
