Napaka-prick niya.

252
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:34,772
Never siyang nag-oo ng nakangiti.

253
00:13:34,855 --> 00:13:35,981
Yung batang brat.

254
00:13:36,065 --> 00:13:37,775
Hoy, matandang brat!

255
00:13:38,359 --> 00:13:42,029
Kahit mahinang magsalita,
tinutulungan niya kami sa lahat ng bagay.

256
00:13:42,112 --> 00:13:43,864
Hindi mo siya dapat tratuhin ng ganyan.

257
00:13:43,948 --> 00:13:45,032
-Tama siya!
-Oo!

258
00:13:45,115 --> 00:13:46,242
ISANG ARAW
SA KULUNGAN NG BAKA NI JONG-IL

259
00:13:46,325 --> 00:13:47,743
Isa, dalawa, tatlo, hilahin!

260
00:13:47,826 --> 00:13:49,286
Hilahin!

261
00:13:49,370 --> 00:13:51,956
Okay. Isa, dalawa, tatlo, hilahin!

262
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,462
-Mukhang maayos ang ngipin.
-Iyan ay isang kaluwagan.

263
00:13:58,546 --> 00:14:00,172
UNERUPTED TEETH
NATATAKPAN PA NG LAGI

